ype":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":12,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"日常科研中，经常会接触不同格式的波形数据，最常见的是 SAC 和 miniSEED 格式。\n每种数据格式都有各自的优点和缺点。例如，SAC 格式有利于数据处理和分析，\n但不利于大批量数据的存储和交换。miniSEED 格式有利于波形数据的存档和交换，\n近几年也常用于数据处理和分析，因此，miniSEED 格式是目前地震学领域","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"wG2K7LPQ5m"},{"type":"strong","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最流行","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"IJFL7hCboH"}],"key":"pMdbxaoJKk"},{"type":"text","value":"的波形数据格式。","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":1},"end":{"line":9,"column":1}},"key":"ApUSh2E1BS"}],"key":"PcedQUJ4V7"},{"type":"heading","depth":2,"position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SAC","position":{"start":{"line":14,"column":1},"end":{"line":14,"column":1}},"key":"jQL3uHgeO2"}],"identifier":"sac","label":"SAC","html_id":"sac","implicit":true,"key":"puwlUigHuf"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":18,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SAC 格式由 ","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"key":"d44gmgT6On"},{"type":"link","url":"https://ds.iris.edu/ds/nodes/dmc/software/downloads/SAC/","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"SAC","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"key":"Aeyt6xWfGh"}],"urlSource":"https://ds.iris.edu/ds/nodes/dmc/software/downloads/SAC/","key":"rH1cjn2H52"},{"type":"text","value":"\n（Seismic Analysis Codes）软件定义，但许多其他软件也支持该格式。每个 SAC 文件包含头段区\n和时间序列数据区，其中头段区定义了与台站、事件、走时以及用户自定义信息等相关的变量。","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1},"end":{"line":16,"column":1}},"key":"srS0KqZ1jf"}],"key":"lsSEKO6dFD"},{"type":"paragraph","position":{"start":{"line":20,"co